# 快速上手

## 1. 创建插件脚手架
:::TuffCodeBlock{lang="bash"}
---
code: |
  pnpm dlx create-tuff-plugin my-plugin
  cd my-plugin
  pnpm install
---
:::
脚手架会生成 Manifest、`index.js` 先导脚本、可选 UI 目录与基础构建配置。

## 2. Manifest
在 `manifest.json` 中先声明插件身份、入口、SDK 版本、分类、权限与 CoreBox feature。

:::TuffCodeBlock{lang="json"}
---
code: |
  {
    "id": "com.example.my-plugin",
    "name": "my-plugin",
    "version": "0.1.0",
    "author": "Example",
    "sdkapi": 260626,
    "category": "utilities",
    "description": "Return a copy action from CoreBox.",
    "main": "index.js",
    "dev": { "enable": true },
    "permissions": {
      "required": [],
      "optional": ["clipboard.write"]
    },
    "permissionReasons": {
      "clipboard.write": "将处理后的文本复制到剪贴板"
    },
    "features": [
      {
        "id": "my-plugin.copy",
        "name": "复制输入文本",
        "desc": "在 CoreBox 中输入文本并复制",
        "keywords": ["copy", "text", "复制"],
        "push": true,
        "acceptedInputTypes": ["text"],
        "commands": [
          { "type": "over", "value": ["copy", "复制"] }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
---
:::

## 3. 先导脚本
`index.js` 运行在插件沙箱中，通过 `globalThis` 访问上下文 API。

:::TuffCodeBlock{lang="javascript"}
---
code: |
  const { clipboard, box, TuffItemBuilder } = globalThis
  const PLUGIN_NAME = 'my-plugin'
  const COPY_ACTION_ID = 'copy'

  function getQueryText(query) {
    return typeof query === 'string' ? query : query?.text ?? ''
  }

  module.exports = {
    async onFeatureTriggered(featureId, query) {
      const text = getQueryText(query).trim()
      if (!text) {
        return []
      }

      return [
        new TuffItemBuilder('my-plugin.copy-result')
          .setSource('plugin', 'plugin-features', PLUGIN_NAME)
          .setTitle('复制输入文本')
          .setSubtitle(text.slice(0, 80))
          .setMeta({
            pluginName: PLUGIN_NAME,
            featureId,
            defaultAction: COPY_ACTION_ID,
          })
          .createAndAddAction(COPY_ACTION_ID, 'copy', '复制', text)
          .build(),
      ]
    },

    async onItemAction(item) {
      const action = item.actions?.find(action => action.id === COPY_ACTION_ID || action.type === 'copy')
      if (action?.payload) {
        clipboard.writeText(action.payload)
      }
      box?.hide?.()
    },
  }
---
:::

## 4. 调试
- 在 `pnpm core:dev` 运行时，插件保存即热重载。
- 调试输出位于 DevTools Console 与 `logs/plugins/<id>.log`。
- 使用 `logger` 输出插件日志，避免把敏感参数写入日志。

## 5. 校验与打包
:::TuffCodeBlock{lang="bash"}
---
code: |
  tuff validate --strict
  tuff build
---
:::
`tuff build` 会输出 `dist/build/` 和 `.tpex` 插件包。发布前继续执行 `tuff publish --dry-run` 预览上传内容。

继续阅读：[插件开发任务流](./plugin-workflow.zh.md)。
